The '''Bonadan Alien Quarter''' was a district in [[Bonadan/Legends|Bonadan's]] [[Spaceport Southeast II]] that contained many businesses and facilities that accommodated the needs and desires of non-Human travelers. The Bonadan Alien Quarter's size and variety of diversions, as well as its reputation as a considerably rough area, resulted in its status as the most well-known [[alien quarter]] in [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

